CSS for Styling
Create a file named style.css inside the static folder


body {
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 20px;
}

header {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}

header nav a {
    margin-right: 20px;
}

.products {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.product {
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
    padding: 10px;
    margin: 10px;
    width: 200px;
}
